Stocks App
----------

FEATURES

Home Page
- See status of stocks (snapshot of stocks vs index)
- Chart that shows real time perfomance of stocks

Portfolio Management
- Trading stocks
- Pie graphs of stock allocations
- Look at each of your stocks

Analytics
- Performance of stocks (how your stocks compare to industry)
- Charts from Google API
- Search for a certain stock
- Sort stocks


JSON FILE

Ticker (string)
Company name (string)
Current stock price (array of floats)
Historical stock price (array of floats)


STOCK FUNCTIONS

Daily change (difference between yesterday's and most current price)
Daily high, daily low
3 month, 6 month, high and low
Average performance of all stocks
Buy stock, Sell stock
